"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-02-12-marathon-world-record-holder-kelvin-kiptum-kenya-dies-24\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Kenyan runner Kelvin Kiptum, the marathon world record holder, died in a car crash Sunday night at age 24.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiptum was driving the car with his coach,\\u00c2\\u00a0Gervais Hakizimana, as a passenger, in the village of\\u00c2\\u00a0Kaptagat in western Kenya when the car veered off the road and ran into a tree.\\u00c2\\u00a0Hakizimana also was killed.\\u00c2\\u00a0A woman was also in the car, and she was taken to a hospital with serious injuries,according to theAssociated Press.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\", \"score\": 0.999999043921664, \"rank\": 9.560791902708942e-07, \"text\": \"Gervais\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricky_Gervais\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999984481747, \"rank\": 9.778033300564177e-10, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiptum\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world record of\\u00c2\\u00a02:00.35\\u00c2\\u00a0was set in October at the Chicago Marathon.\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The record officially was ratified by\\u00c2\\u00a0international track federation World Athletics just last week.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.999999997452278, \"rank\": 2.547719431487449e-09, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi